'''Al-Bourj Football Club Beirut''' ({{lang-ar|البرج}}), or simply '''Al-Bourj''', is a [[Lebanon|Lebanese]] [[association football|football]] club its based in [[Bourj el-Barajneh]], [[Beirut]]. The club competes in the [[Lebanese Second Division]].

