Starting in the [[1945 All-American Girls Professional Baseball League season|1945 season]], on its third year of operation, the [[All-American Girls Professional Baseball League]] honored with the [[Player of the year award|Player of the Year Award]] the top performer in the circuit. The AAGPBL folded at the end of the 1954 season. This is the list of winners.
