'''Belize Defence Force Football Club''' is a [[Belize]]an [[Association football|football]] team which currently competes in the [[Premier League of Belize]] of the [[Football Federation of Belize]]. It is sponsored by the country's [[Belize Defence Force|national army]] of the same name. The Belize Defence Force F.C (or "Military Football Machine" as they are known at the national level) have won the Belize Premier Football League National Championship three times; the 2009–2010 Opening season,
the [[2009–10 Belize Premier Football League#Closing Season|2009–10 Closing season]], and the [[2010–11 Belize Premier Football League|2010–11 Opening season]].

The team is based in [[Belize]]. Their home stadium is [[MCC Grounds (stadium)|MCC Grounds]].

