'''Estadio Camping Resort''' is a [[Football (Soccer)|Football]] stadium in [[Chilibre]], [[Panamá Province]] who hosts [[ANAPROF]] team [[Alianza F.C. (Panama)|Alianza F.C.]] since 2001.
