{{Unreferenced|date=January 2007}}
'''Estadio Municipal Pedro Román Meléndez''' (English: Pedro Román Meléndez Municipal Stadium) is a multi-use [[stadium]] in [[Manatí, Puerto Rico|Manatí]], [[Puerto Rico]].  It is currently used mostly for [[baseball]] games and is the home of [[Atenienses de Manatí]].  The stadium holds 8,500 people.

