GET Arena is a [[kart racing]] venue in [[Victoria Island, Lagos]]. The venue also incorporates eateries among other facilities as an event center to host social gatherings.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://guardian.ng/life/travel-and-places/five-places-to-visit-in-lagos-today/|title=Five places to visit in Lagos today|publisher=The Guardian|access-date=August 14, 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://allafrica.com/stories/201102150843.html|title=Nigeria: GET Arena Hosts Turbotuesday|publisher=This day|website=AllAfrica|access-date=August 14, 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.pulse.ng/lifestyle/food-travel-arts-culture/affordable-fun-10-exciting-ways-to-have-fun-in-lagos-with-n5-000-id7338580.html|title=10 exciting ways to have fun in Lagos|publisher=Pulse|access-date=August 14, 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.tripadvisor.com/Attraction_Review-g2492082-d6898517-Reviews-GET_Arena-Lekki_Lagos_State.html|website=[[TripAdvisor]]|title=GET Arena, Lekki, Lagos|access-date=August 14, 2018}}</ref>

