The '''Six Days of Fiorenzuola''' is a [[Six-day racing|six-day track cycling race]] held annually in [[Fiorenzuola]], [[Italy]]. The event was first held in 1998.<ref>http://www.memoire-du-cyclisme.eu/piste_6jours/6j_fiorenzuola_arda.php</ref>

